snippet.title: CODE VEIN – DLC #3 Lord of Thunder
snippet.description:
You fought against the rulers of fire & ice but are you prepared to face the Lord of Thunder? #CODEVEIN


DLC 3 #LordofThunder is available now! This new DLC comes with new weapons, stage, items, and a new boss! Rise up #Revenant your fight is not over. https://bandainam.co/CV2
